-- Salini May Have Matched Gavio’s Stake in Impregilo, Sole Reports
-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 2012-04-21T12:09:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-21/salini-may-have-matched-gavio-s-stake-in-impregilo-sole-reports.html
Salini Costruttori SpA may have
increased its stake in builder  Impregilo SpA (IPG)  to “slightly
more” than 29 percent, matching the holding of Gavio Group,  Il
Sole 24 Ore  reported, without saying how it got the information.  Salini is set to present an integration plan with
Impregilo, prepared with its advisers Rothschild and Boston
Consulting Group, on April 23, Sole said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  